The paper discusses security and privacy concerns in computer systems, and proposes new mechanisms that take advantage of Trusted Execution Environments (TEEs) for distributed system architectures. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Computer Security (cs.CR), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CY).
